Rating: 3
A very simple risotto and a very good side dish. I would recommend adding a little more saffron (1/2 tsp instead of 1/4 tsp) and to do it a little earlier than 3 min before completion in order to give the aromatic flavor and yellow color more time to permeate the dish. Also, a little grey salt added in beginning would be helpful. I'm definitely keeping this recipe to accompany fish and chicken.

